        "text": "Verse 22.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "And I saw no temple therein: for the Lord God Almighty and the Lamb are the temple of it.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " No ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "ναός",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", \"inner shrine,\" or \"sanctuary\" (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Revelation 7:15",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). The whole city is now the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "ναός",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (cf. on vers. 16, 17, where the shape of the city is that of the holy of holies). The presence of God pervades all the city (cf. ver. 11); all the redeemed are within the sanctuary, all are now priests (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Revelation 20:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). There is, therefore, no ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greek",
        "text": "ναός",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", or \"temple,\" within the city, for the whole city itself is the temple. The Object of all worship and the great Sacrifice are there (Alford). Revelation 21:22",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
